    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a little bit generic. I need it to hit harder on the specific threats. Can you add a section that really calls out how these progressive policies—like the push for new gender ideologies in schools and the breakdown of the nuclear family structure—are actually dangerous to the stability of our kids' futures? Don't hold back, we need to make the voters feel the urgency.",
